snippet.title: Eternal Fate for PC and Mac
snippet.description:
Join the world of Eternal Fate!  Launching on Steam November 5th 2015!

Now supporting Gaming Tribe Connection!

Collect hundreds of mighty heroes and defeat the Corruption from your PC or mobile devices. Whether you want to roll through endless dungeons with your guild, or battle it out in multiple PvP arenas, Eternal Fate has something for you.

Eternal Fate on Steam: http://bit.ly/ef_steam 

Download for iOS today!
http://bit.ly/EternalFateiOS

Download for Android today!
http://bit.ly/EternalFateAndroid

Eternal Fate PC & Mac Press release: http://bit.ly/ef_steam_announcement
